Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\bord2\pos(470,640)}세이버
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,어차피 가짜 놈한테는\N고작해야 그게 한계인가
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,검이여
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,차오르라!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,'보구'인가
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,좋지
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,마스터한테서\N허가도 떨어졌겠다
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,이쪽도 보구로\N대항해보도록 할까
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,처형 시간이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,가짜 놈에게 걸맞는
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,최후를 맞이하도록 하여라!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,간다, {\blur7\bord5\3c&H282828&}"흑"{\r}의 세이버!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,와라
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\bord5\3c&H2E2FFF&}"적"{\r}의 세이버!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,압제에 반역을!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,압제에 통렬한 고통을!
